KPI: Year Over Year Units Available 9

Units Available

Drag and Drop fields in Text Mark  (Fields;  Units Available, cc. YoY Units Available, cc. YoY Units Down , cc. YoY Units Up)

Edit as in gif


Formatting the Labels with Color, Font and Size

1  - Select each field and format it  (Details are given below)

2  - Select Color     

3 - Select More Color   

4 - Copy and paste the given color code   

5 - Click OK

Do the same for each field then  6 Click Apply to see if all of them match that in the snapshot.

If it does Press OK 7 


Format Details 

Units Available                     - Size 8

<SUM(Units Available)>       - Size 26    -  #006c84   

<AGG(cc.YoY Units DOWN)> - Size 9     -  #c60000

<AGG(cc.YoY Units UP)>                -  Size 9      -  #59a14f  

<AGG(cc.YoY Units Available)> vs PY -  Size 9   -  #c16941 


Format & Deactivate Tooltip

Click Text Mark to Center,  Right click SUM(Units Available) to format, Right Click AGG(cc. YoY Units Available) to Format, Click on Tooltip to de activate it by unchecking the boxes.
